    "en": {
      "title": "Water cut tomorrow in Colombo",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NWSDB) has announced that an 11-hour water cut has been implemented in some parts of Colombo.",
        "Accordingly, tomorrow Saturday (30) from 09.00 pm to Sunday (31) 8.00 am water cut will be implemented.",
        "Water cut will be implemented in Colombo 9, 10, 11 and 12.",
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board has informed that the water supply will be cut off due to the rectification works."
      ],
